Pigeon Training Toothbrush Lesson-1 (Light Blue) Price: Rs.135

When infants are around six months of age their first milk teeth start to appear. It is mandatory to start their dental hygiene routine in the beginning itself. Though your tiny tot may not be eating any solid food or any food other than mother’s milk there is a high chance of tooth decay from the natural sugars found in breast milk. To prevent this and to ensure that your bundle of joy has the best smile with healthy glistening white teeth you have to clean their teeth regularly. Pigeon’s Training Toothbrush Lesson 1 has been crafted especially for babies of six to eight months of age.

The elastic rubber head of this Pigeon Training Toothbrush will brush gently against your bundle of joy’s tender gums massaging them softly. The handle is made with a very contoured design that makes it easy for you to hold and brush your baby’s teeth with care and precision. When using this toothbrush make sure that the shield is attached so that the brush does not go deep into the infant’s mouth and cause choking.

Pigeon Children Toothpaste - Strawberry (45 g) Price: Rs.100

Children are always fussy about brushing their teeth. Getting them to brush and clean their teeth can be very taxing as the young toddlers get bored of the minty flavors easily. But without proper cleaning your tiny tots can develop painful cavities. The Strawberry flavor of the Pigeon’s Children Toothpaste will grab your infant’s attention. This aspect of this Children’s Toothpaste will ease your efforts in convincing your little one to brush her teeth.

The low foam Pigeon Toothpaste helps in preventing tooth decay and maintaining healthy gums. Since only a limited amount of foam is formed by this Pigeon Toothpaste there are less chances of your baby swallowing the foam. To guarantee healthy gums and teeth to your tiny tot make sure that they brush properly twice a day. This Pigeon Children’s Toothpaste with Strawberry flavor is suitable for children between the ages of one and six. Ensure adult supervision while using pastes

Pigeon Training Toothbrush Lesson-1 (Light Pink) Price: Rs.195

A smile can brighten the darkest day
column17: but we all know that we have to work on those smiles as early as possible to keep them shining bright. The Pigeon Training Toothbrush Lesson-1 is a baby toothbrush that is specially designed to help your baby get on a proper oral hygiene regimen. Suitable for babies aged 7 months and above
column18:
this training toothbrush is for babies with 2 to 3 milk teeth. The toothbrush has a soft elastomer rubber head that comfortably fits your baby\u2019s mouth and is gentle on their sensitive gums and teeth.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe lesson-1 toothbrush has a thick and contoured handle that facilitates easy grip and makes it easy for your baby to get used to brushing movements. The toothbrush comes with a special shield that can be locked onto the handle of the brush to prevent your baby from accidentally swallowing the brush
column19:
chocking or gagging. The shield can also be used as a base to hold the brush after brushing is done. The unique\xa0Pigeon Training Toothbrush Lesson-1 is an ideal toothbrush that helps in properly cleaning teeth and gums and sets your baby on the path to a brighter smile.

\n
\n ']
